{
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest1012191390670040804.description1":"&7攻击敌人并提供&a回避&7状态。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest1012191390670040804.subtitle":"感觉不如厕纸",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest1012191390670040804.task.4510043995094703391.title":"看向一个木乃伊使魔",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest1012191390670040804.title":"&6木乃伊使魔",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest1077895186596553283.description1":"&7召唤一只&5被附身的远古守卫者&7，它能够掉落&62-4个鹦鹉螺壳&7，还有&640%%的几率&7掉落一个&1海洋之心&7。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest1077895186596553283.subtitle":"非常古老的鱼类",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest1077895186596553283.title":"&6被附身的远古守卫者",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest1220691420592144448.description1":"&7首先，将一些&2橡树树苗&7扔进你的&5灵火&7——最好多扔几个，以备不时之需。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest1220691420592144448.description2":"&7下一步，把它们种下来，耐心等待生长。这些树苗看上去没什么特别的，但是对魔灵来说，他们&d神秘&7又&d重要&7。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest1220691420592144448.description3":"&7树苗长成后，吃下一颗&d魔鬼之梦果&7，窥视魔灵眼中的世界。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest1220691420592144448.description4":"&7在眼前的世界发生变化后，收集&6原木&7并返回现实…",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest1220691420592144448.description5":"&7不要尝试把什么…&4<shake>“朋友”&7带回来。这非常…不合时宜，起码现在是。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest1220691420592144448.subtitle":"一面镜子",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest1220691420592144448.title":"&6异界",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest1418623224976930640.description1":"&7可以&b骑乘&7。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest1418623224976930640.subtitle":"超载",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest1418623224976930640.task.4664069273149262091.title":"看向一个奇美拉使魔",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest1418623224976930640.title":"&6奇美拉使魔",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest171321395067566411.description1":"&7通过召唤&6仪式&7，你甚至可以控制&e时间&7！",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest171321395067566411.subtitle":"改变地球自转",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest171321395067566411.title":"时间",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest1721105767395931891.description1":"&7该仪式能将&e时间&7设置为&6黎明&7。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest1721105767395931891.subtitle":"早上好",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest1721105767395931891.task.6045639436381898081.title":"任意#balm:yellow_dyes",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest1721105767395931891.title":"&6破晓黎明",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest1840050031300507780.description1":"&7啊，&f粉笔&7…唤起我的回忆~",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest1840050031300507780.description2":"&7要合成你自己的&f粉笔&7，首先要将&6异界原木&7和&6异界石&7放进&6熔炉&7。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest1840050031300507780.description3":"&7将它们烧成&c异界灰烬&7和&c煅烧异界石&7，然后在&6工作台&7合成&f粉笔&7！",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest1840050031300507780.description4":"&7然而不幸的是…你的手艺不够好。&7人类总是如此。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest1840050031300507780.description5":"&7好啦，把粉笔拿出来——扔进&5灵火&7里，我来给你弄干净。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest1840050031300507780.description6":"&7只需要一小会儿。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest1840050031300507780.subtitle":"粉笔画",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest1840050031300507780.title":"&6童年回忆",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest1958989025882807954.description1":"&7你知道你的&6碎矿者&7能够提高矿石产出吗？",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest1958989025882807954.description2":"&7如果是&b精准采集&7下来的矿石，产出量会更多！",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest1958989025882807954.subtitle":"更多产出！",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest1958989025882807954.task.1920266029211070068.title":"&6你知道吗？",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest1958989025882807954.title":"&e你知道吗？",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest2036973968081999008.description1":"&7挖矿时修复装备，&a升级其他使魔&7。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest2036973968081999008.subtitle":"修补2：铁匠再临",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest2036973968081999008.task.7280311434857189658.title":"看向一个铁匠使魔",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest2036973968081999008.title":"&6铁匠使魔",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest20701095601415897.description1":"&6魔精&7是最弱的&d魔灵&7，与其他魔灵相比，他们会随时间&c缓慢衰退&7。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest20701095601415897.description2":"&e潜行右击&7你的&6魔精&7，即可查看它的&c衰退状态&7。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest20701095601415897.subtitle":"灵髓衰退",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest20701095601415897.task.8050854788647581289.title":"&e魔精衰朽",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest2129076153642739630.description1":"&7感觉还是太慢？试试束缚一只&1魔王&7——&d异界&7最强大的魔灵。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest2129076153642739630.description2":"&7几乎没有人能够成功束缚它们……",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest2129076153642739630.description3":"&7我会……&4<shake>尽量不让它们心烦&7。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest2129076153642739630.subtitle":"魔王",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest2129076153642739630.title":"&6挖矿大师",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest2262342022787814739.description1":"&7向玩家提供&e夜视&7。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest2262342022787814739.subtitle":"这是为了看到更遥远的境界",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest2262342022787814739.task.5870557737581365791.title":"看向一个蝙蝠使魔",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest2262342022787814739.title":"&6蝙蝠使魔",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest2502814531562275668.description1":"&7&2魔王碎矿者&7是效率最高的碎矿者，能够显著地将产出提高到每个矿石&b四&7到&b六个矿粉&7。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest2502814531562275668.subtitle":"口袋藏沙",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest2502814531562275668.title":"&6魔王碎矿者",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest2550208942984800839.description1":"&7召唤一只&5被附身的末影人&7，它能够掉落&61-3个末影珍珠&7。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest2550208942984800839.subtitle":"末影弹球",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest2550208942984800839.title":"&6被附身的末影人",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest2607923544294834026.description1":"&7你需要合成&6献祭之碗&7，将物品献祭给魔灵。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest2607923544294834026.description2":"&7用之前剩下的&6异界石&7合成就行。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest2607923544294834026.subtitle":"祭品",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest2607923544294834026.title":"&6不是用来盛麦片的",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest2637307830050767066.description1":"&7高亮敌人并发射&c激光&7。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest2637307830050767066.subtitle":"太阳其实是一个致命的激光发射器",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest2637307830050767066.task.3286050423392681133.title":"看向一个眼魔使魔",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest2637307830050767066.title":"&6眼魔使魔",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest267136015529809870.description1":"&7是时候创造一个&a朋友&7了！",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest267136015529809870.description2":"&7我们需要先找到它们，然后才能绘制我们的第一个&5五芒星&7，开始召唤仪式。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest267136015529809870.description3":"&7幸运的是，在&d异界&7，找到它们很简单！",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest267136015529809870.description4":"&7只要将一本&f书&7、一根&f羽毛&7和一个&0黑色染料&7扔进&5灵火&7。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest267136015529809870.description5":"&7然后，将产物与&f四个白色染料&7合成&6绑定之书：魔精&7。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest267136015529809870.description6":"&7合成出来的绑定之书还是未绑定的——你需要将未绑定的书与你的&b魔灵全典&7合成，完成绑定。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest267136015529809870.description7":"&7现在，你的好朋友已经和这本书连在一起了，虽说你现在还看不到它们…",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest267136015529809870.description8":"&7别担心——我们马上就来揭晓你的新同伴！",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest267136015529809870.subtitle":"绑定朋友",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest267136015529809870.title":"&6你的第一次绑定",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest2787037916820239546.description1":"&7召唤一只&5被附身的幻翼&7，它能够掉落&61-4个幻翼膜&7。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest2787037916820239546.subtitle":"起飞",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest2787037916820239546.title":"&6被附身的幻翼",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest2875744021073382785.description1":"&7召唤一只&5被附身的监守者&7，它能够掉落&11个回响碎片&7。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest2875744021073382785.subtitle":"踏入深渊",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest2875744021073382785.title":"&6被附身的监守者",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest2912427702379283997.description1":"&7该仪式能将&b天气&7设置为&e晴天&7。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest2912427702379283997.subtitle":"拨开云层",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest2912427702379283997.title":"&6晴空万里",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest3051557231097527763.description1":"&7提供&c有条件的伤害加成&7。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest3051557231097527763.subtitle":"鸡骑士",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest3051557231097527763.task.7240171240314663058.title":"看向一个无头鼠骑士使魔",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest3051557231097527763.title":"&6无头鼠骑士使魔",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest3123554205055172650.description1":"&7&6魔灵同调宝石&7在仪式中至关重要。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest3123554205055172650.description2":"&7遗憾的是，对你们人类来说，他们非常昂贵！",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest3123554205055172650.description3":"&7将&b钻石&7扔进&5灵火&7就能得到魔灵同调宝石。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest3123554205055172650.description4":"&7你需要至少&a九个&7才能继续下一步——以后要的会更多！",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest3123554205055172650.subtitle":"魔灵同调宝石",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest3123554205055172650.title":"&6异界宝石",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest3291834807054458991.description1":"&7&6魔精搬运工&7是一种可以在容器间&e运输物品&7的召唤魔灵，能够作为一个简单而有效的&b物流&7工具。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest3291834807054458991.subtitle":"物品运输",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest3291834807054458991.title":"&6魔精搬运工",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest3347267177474104533.description1":"&7自动拾取物品，&a提升拾取范围&7。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest3347267177474104533.subtitle":"<shake>把金子给那个地精！",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest3347267177474104533.task.4501103943063983129.title":"看向一个贪婪使魔",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest3347267177474104533.title":"&6贪婪使魔",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest3404518807669471084.subtitle":"&4<shake>永远&7在一起",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest3404518807669471084.task.8481179894188296264.title":"看向一个恶魔丈夫",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest3404518807669471084.title":"&d恶魔婚礼",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest3410710614041377438.description1":"&7召唤一只&5被附身的孱弱潜影贝&7，它能够掉落&61-3个紫颂果&7，还有&a10%%的几率&7掉落一个&5潜影壳&7。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest3410710614041377438.subtitle":"弱弱",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest3410710614041377438.title":"&6被附身的孱弱潜影贝",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest3506934891250771886.description1":"&7谁能想到你能在&d异界&7存储物品呢？",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest3506934891250771886.description2":"&7举行几个&5仪式&7你就能制作出一个&6维度存储促动器&7——在&b魔灵全典&7上查看具体详情。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest3506934891250771886.description3":"&7它拥有&a128个格子&7，每个格子能够容纳最多&a1024个物品&7！",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest3506934891250771886.subtitle":"将物品存在异界！",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest3506934891250771886.title":"维度存储！",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest352171864690532200.description1":"&7接下来，再获取一个&d魔鬼之梦种子&7，种在&6耕地&7上。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest352171864690532200.description2":"&7待到完全成熟后，收获结出的&d果实&7——谁能想到做梦竟然如此简单！",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest352171864690532200.subtitle":"黑暗的果实",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest352171864690532200.title":"&6魔鬼之梦果",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest3594066650940302713.description1":"&7虽然无法看见异界的全貌，稍微&a瞥视&7几眼还是能够做到的。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest3594066650940302713.description2":"&7你早已体会过这种感觉，虽然只是短短片刻……",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest3594066650940302713.description3":"&7难道你不想再多探索一会&d异界&7？真走运，我手里就有你需要的东西！",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest3594066650940302713.description4":"&7制作这副&6眼镜&7，它能够起到&f魔鬼之梦&7同样的效果——只要戴上就会永久持续。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest3594066650940302713.description5":"&7而且，不会有魔鬼之梦果那样的扭曲效果！",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest3594066650940302713.subtitle":"窥视世界的彼端",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest3594066650940302713.task.6516456238265558932.title":"异界眼镜",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest3594066650940302713.title":"&6异界视野",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest3635146049401499018.description1":"&7将之前制作的材料按顺序放置在碗中，即可开启你的第一个&5仪式&7。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest3635146049401499018.description2":"&7别担心——你的&b魔灵全典&7上写着正确的顺序呢！",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest3635146049401499018.description3":"&7我还可以帮你将仪式投影出来——在仪式页面点击左下角的&e眼睛&7图标即可。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest3635146049401499018.description4":"&7一切就绪后，献祭你的物品，并等待你的新&a朋友&7来收取。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest3635146049401499018.description5":"&7欢迎回家，&a朋友&7！",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest3635146049401499018.subtitle":"欢迎新朋友！",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest3635146049401499018.task.7002607421791384888.title":"任意#forge:raw_materials/silver",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest3635146049401499018.title":"&4永恒的伙伴",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest3712230994747249086.subtitle":"&4<shake>永远&7在一起",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest3712230994747249086.task.5402496098380609455.title":"看向一个恶魔妻子",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest3712230994747249086.title":"&d恶魔婚礼",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest3767427217424758774.description1":"&7灵魂宝石&7能够在保存生物完整&cNBT&7的情况下搬运它们。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest3767427217424758774.description2":"&7在运输&5仪式&7祭品时尤其好用。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest3767427217424758774.subtitle":"异界牢笼",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest3767427217424758774.title":"&6灵魂宝石",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest3904327047552619806.description1":"&6欢迎来到&5神秘学&6！",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest3904327047552619806.description2":"&5神秘学&7模组能够帮助你自动化各种事项，高效地存储物品，并深入探索由仪式和&4魔灵&7构成的奇妙世界。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest3904327047552619806.description3":"&7开始你的神秘学之旅，首先要找到&d魔鬼之梦种子&7，打草就能获得。获得魔鬼之梦种子后，你就能合成属于自己的&b魔灵全典&7——探索&5异界&7的必备指南！",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest3904327047552619806.subtitle":"神秘学简介",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest3904327047552619806.title":"&6魔灵全典",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest4044484924216062876.description1":"&7&f凋灵骷髅头颅&7是许多&5五芒星仪式&7的刚需。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest4044484924216062876.description2":"&7一种获取凋零骷髅头的方式是通过&5奥索林的无约束呼唤&7——需要用到一个先前收集的&f骷髅头颅&7。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest4044484924216062876.description3":"&7要小心：&5狂猎&7会召唤一些&c高等魔灵&7。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest4044484924216062876.description4":"&o&7准备万全后再面对它们！",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest4044484924216062876.subtitle":"凋灵的头颅",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest4044484924216062876.title":"&6凋灵骷髅头颅",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest4157103097207323553.description1":"&7&2提升原木破坏速度&7。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest4157103097207323553.subtitle":"奇普木材公司",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest4157103097207323553.task.1575461095302342467.title":"看向一个河狸使魔",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest4157103097207323553.title":"&6河狸使魔",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest4312593453813538688.description1":"&7哈？！你真需要存那么多东西吗？",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest4312593453813538688.description2":"&7也许你应该清理一下开间——我看那些&6胸甲&7你从来都没碰过！",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest4312593453813538688.description3":"&7你知道每次你扔一堆垃圾过来我都要挨个分好类吗？",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest4312593453813538688.description4":"&7算了……你还可以再升级，没错。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest4312593453813538688.description5":"&7但这次就不会那么简单了——你需要打败&a植物魔法&7的&d盖亚&7。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest4312593453813538688.subtitle":"还要更多？！",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest4312593453813538688.title":"&6等级3存储稳定器",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest4361000769903417863.description1":"&7召唤一只&5被附身的潜影贝&7，它能够掉落&61-2个潜影壳&7。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest4361000769903417863.subtitle":"末影背包",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest4361000769903417863.title":"&6被附身的潜影贝",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest4415590285755942549.description1":"&7&6异界石交易者&7可用各种石头交换&6异界石&7，比从&5灵火&7里得到的更多。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest4415590285755942549.subtitle":"异界矿工",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest4415590285755942549.title":"&6异界石交易者",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest4481823838795305522.description1":"&7使用&5海德林诱惑术&7召唤&6被附身的骷髅&7，击杀以获取&f骷髅头颅&7。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest4481823838795305522.description2":"&7如果仪式无法启动，原因很简单——&7&d仪式需要祭品&7。在仪式附近献祭一只&f鸡&7来满足神灵。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest4481823838795305522.subtitle":"骷髅头颅",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest4481823838795305522.title":"&6被附身的骷髅",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest4485231607013917791.description1":"&7通过召唤&6仪式&7，你甚至可以控制世界中的&b天气&7！",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest4485231607013917791.subtitle":"操控云层",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest4485231607013917791.title":"&6天气控制",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest4537214647687518408.description1":"&7&e火灵碎矿者&7效率更高，每个矿石能粉碎出&b四个矿粉&7。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest4537214647687518408.subtitle":"粉末飞扬",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest4537214647687518408.title":"&6火灵碎矿者",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest4587507024651630646.description1":"&7已经做出&6矿井&7了？但是不知道怎么用？",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest4587507024651630646.description2":"&7啊，当然——能量可不会凭空产生！",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest4587507024651630646.description3":"&7你需要有人替你挖矿。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest4587507024651630646.description4":"&7将一只&d巨灵&7束缚在&6神灯&7中，让它给你卖命！",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest4587507024651630646.subtitle":"挖矿随从",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest4587507024651630646.title":"&6自动挖矿",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest4892139822301257682.description1":"&7存活时防止&c玩家死亡&7。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest4892139822301257682.subtitle":"并非鱼。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest4892139822301257682.task.4859684699520894713.title":"看向一个守护者使魔",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest4892139822301257682.title":"&6守护者使魔",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest5119197271193239732.description1":"&7召唤一只&5被附身的疣猪兽&7，它能够掉落&c一个锻造模板&7，或者&c一个下界合金碎片&7，或者&8什么也不掉&7。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest5119197271193239732.subtitle":"下界猪",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest5119197271193239732.title":"&6被附身的疣猪兽",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest522835088136680408.description1":"&7还要更多！不！不能再多了！",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest522835088136680408.description2":"&7我已经能在你的宝库里游泳了！",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest522835088136680408.description3":"&7幸运的是，除非你击败&5龙&7，否则休想把我淹死在这里。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest522835088136680408.description4":"&7哈哈~没有什么&6蜜蜂女王&7刚刚给了你一些&5龙息&7……吧？",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest522835088136680408.subtitle":"&4<shake>够了！",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest522835088136680408.title":"&6等级4存储稳定器",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest5259967167041650647.description1":"&7这枚&6戒指&7能够将关在其中的&6使魔&7的效果施加给穿戴者，不需要再召唤出来了。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest5259967167041650647.subtitle":"便携式使魔",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest5259967167041650647.title":"&6使魔之戒",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest5286806532366273216.description1":"&7&5紫色粉笔&7是&5神秘学&7中最后的几个主要粉笔之一。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest5286806532366273216.description2":"&7&4红色粉笔&7也是必需品，但它只在几个仪式中会用到，我们之后再谈。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest5286806532366273216.description3":"&7用你的&6碎矿者魔精&7粉碎&d末地石&7和&5黑曜石&7，用粉碎产物制作&5紫色粉笔&7。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest5286806532366273216.subtitle":"月亮的味道！",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest5286806532366273216.title":"&6紫色粉笔",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest5384342346873650072.description1":"&7向玩家提供&a经验提升&7。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest5384342346873650072.subtitle":"驴子的妻子",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest5384342346873650072.task.8372875426508975149.title":"看向一个龙使魔",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest5384342346873650072.title":"&6龙使魔",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest5423531741248790776.description1":"&7&6交易魔灵&7能够交易主世界和异界的物品。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest5423531741248790776.subtitle":"和魔灵交易",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest5423531741248790776.title":"&6异界商人",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest5797188896009056471.description1":"&7虽然&6“终结之剑”&7不是&5神秘学&7的内容，但它不失为一种极佳的获取&f生物头颅&7的方式。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest5797188896009056471.subtitle":"斩首",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest5797188896009056471.title":"&e终结之剑",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest5797723097557929628.description1":"&7&6魔精伐木工&7，一种基础的召唤魔灵，完美适配游戏前期的工作。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest5797723097557929628.description2":"&7它会&2自动砍树&7并&a种植树苗&7，为你达成简单的&b原木自动化&7。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest5797723097557929628.subtitle":"异界伐木工",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest5797723097557929628.title":"&6魔精伐木工",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest6036883962725139539.description1":"&7啊……我已经履行了指引你&5神秘学&7的&6合同义务&7了。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest6036883962725139539.description2":"&7哦？你以为我是自愿帮忙的？&a哈哈！&7别逗我笑了。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest6036883962725139539.description3":"&7没必要的话我才不会来！",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest6036883962725139539.description4":"&7所以……祝你好运，可千万别死了。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest6036883962725139539.description5":"&7但如果你真的死了……",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest6036883962725139539.description6":"&4<shake>我就在下面等着你。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest6036883962725139539.subtitle":"潜入黑暗",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest6036883962725139539.task.4792963857417040053.title":"探索神秘",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest6036883962725139539.title":"&6探索神秘",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest6078702824296249724.description1":"&7&6机器操作员&7能够将&6存储促动器&7中的物品运输到它管理的机器中，以达成流水线&b自动化&7操作。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest6078702824296249724.subtitle":"经理",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest6078702824296249724.title":"&6巨灵机器操作员",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest6113844826794729525.description1":"&7&6使魔仪式&7能够召唤出忠实的仆从，忠心&c保护&7你——甚至甘于牺牲自己！",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest6113844826794729525.description2":"&7有些使魔是&c强力的守护者&7，还有一些只是待在你身边的&a有用的同伴&7。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest6113844826794729525.subtitle":"为力量而生",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest6113844826794729525.title":"&6使魔",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest6158661938434731233.description1":"&7&6巨灵碎矿者&7与&6魔精碎矿者&7功能类似，但&a不会灵髓衰退&7。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest6158661938434731233.description2":"&7粉碎速度更快，可以将矿石粉碎成&b三个对应的粉&7而不是之前的两个。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest6158661938434731233.subtitle":"美味石头",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest6158661938434731233.task.2955626075762132297.title":"任意#forge:dusts/silver",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest6158661938434731233.task.3255922867245810776.title":"任意#forge:dusts/gold",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest6158661938434731233.task.7993869731228494923.title":"任意#forge:dusts/copper",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest6158661938434731233.task.8591175562242270762.title":"任意#forge:dusts/iron",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest6158661938434731233.title":"&6巨灵碎矿者",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest6275269636594489775.description1":"&7&c红色粉笔&7用来绘制几个大后期的&5仪式&7。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest6275269636594489775.subtitle":"小心烫手",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest6275269636594489775.title":"&c红色粉笔",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest6340534686831243291.description1":"&7确保你的&6存储系统&7处于加载状态——不然它们就没法被访问！",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest6340534686831243291.subtitle":"已加载区块",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest6340534686831243291.task.5748705425427889197.title":"&6小窍门",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest6340534686831243291.title":"&e小窍门",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest6377873408296942791.description1":"&7异界中有&6五种魔灵&7——但只有&6四种&7能够被人类绑定。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest6377873408296942791.description2":"&6魔精&7——最弱，缺少智力，通常用于简单劳作。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest6377873408296942791.description3":"&6巨灵&7——最常用，能够肩负更重要的任务。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest6377873408296942791.description4":"&6火灵&7——强大，具有超出人类的力量和智力，只有技艺最精湛的邪教徒才应该召唤。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest6377873408296942791.description5":"&6魔王&7——能够绑定的最强的魔灵。时刻注意…是他们服侍你，还是你在服侍他们？",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest6377873408296942791.description6":"&6高等魔灵&7——最为强大的存在。它们不可能被绑定到你的破书上，&7不用试都知道。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest6377873408296942791.description7":"&7&o详细信息可以在&b魔灵全典&7上查阅。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest6377873408296942791.subtitle":"五魔灵",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest6377873408296942791.title":"&e绑定之书",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest6431773933614730601.description1":"&7你现在应该理解了&5神秘学&7的基础知识，能够召唤&d更多的魔灵&7——甚至召唤那些强大的魔灵！",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest6431773933614730601.description2":"&7不幸的是，你可能还没集齐某些&5仪式&7需要的特定&6物品&7。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest6431773933614730601.description3":"&7别担心——&5神秘学&7提供了获取这些物品的方式！",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest6431773933614730601.description4":"&7其中最重要的就是&f骷髅头颅&7和&d末地石&7。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest6431773933614730601.subtitle":"前路漫漫",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest6431773933614730601.task.3797719453108169171.title":"不断扩张的神秘学世界",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest6431773933614730601.title":"&6附身基础",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest6481117546110437280.description1":"&7该仪式能将&b天气&7设置为&c雷雨&7。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest6481117546110437280.subtitle":"宙斯",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest6481117546110437280.task.6105641753264883159.title":"任意#forge:bones",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest6481117546110437280.title":"&6震颤",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest653173348705175433.description1":"&7在开始你的第一个仪式前，还有一个步骤要准备——&e蜡烛&7！",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest653173348705175433.description2":"&7要制作蜡烛，你需要灯芯和某种燃料——&4<shake>一些血-&7…&7我是说，一些完全无害的燃料。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest653173348705175433.description3":"&7要获取&6动物油脂&7，首先要制作一把&6屠刀&7，用&f两个铁锭&7和&f三根木棍&7合成。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest653173348705175433.description4":"&7然后，用屠刀狩猎几只动物——它们就会掉落&6动物油脂&7，是不是挺有意思~？",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest653173348705175433.description5":"&7最后，将&f线&7和&6动物油脂&7组合起来，合成属于你自己的&e蜡烛&7！",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest653173348705175433.subtitle":"&4第一滴血",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest653173348705175433.title":"&6屠夫",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest6547098498407627598.description1":"&7你那双低级的人类眼睛已经见过几乎所有看得见的&d异界&7资源了。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest6547098498407627598.description2":"&7但说实话，我认为你可以和恶魔做个交易，获取你看不见的那部分……",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest6547098498407627598.description3":"&7总而言之，这个&6镐子&7可以让你挖掘终极资源！",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest6547098498407627598.subtitle":"灌注镐",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest6547098498407627598.title":"&6易碎矿镐",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest6569490076782776063.description1":"&7存储容量不够了？没问题！",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest6569490076782776063.description2":"&7搭建&6维度存储稳定器&7来扩充空间——最多可以同时使用&a6&7个。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest6569490076782776063.subtitle":"更多存储！",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest6569490076782776063.title":"&6等级1存储稳定器",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest6599728408517321413.description1":"&7提供&b水下呼吸&7。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest6599728408517321413.subtitle":"来自深渊之下",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest6599728408517321413.task.6333387802615747242.title":"看向一个克苏鲁使魔",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest6599728408517321413.title":"&6克苏鲁使魔",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest6648222650915510486.description1":"&7&6附身仪式&7能够召唤出有大用途的强力存在。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest6648222650915510486.description2":"&7它们可以帮你&a跳阶段&7甚至代替&6难以找到的结构&7，对推进度大有裨益。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest6648222650915510486.subtitle":"为死亡而生",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest6648222650915510486.title":"&6附身",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest6718120398882492132.description1":"&7提供&b跳跃提升&7。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest6718120398882492132.subtitle":"未知样本四号",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest6718120398882492132.task.2089548939856260418.title":"看向一个小鹿使魔",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest6718120398882492132.title":"&6小鹿使魔",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest6742842450344683425.description1":"&7&6召唤仪式&7能够为你招来各种魔灵，协助你完成诸多任务——从&a交易&7和&e碎矿&7，到&2伐木&7甚至是&b自动化&7。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest6742842450344683425.subtitle":"为服侍而生",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest6742842450344683425.title":"&6召唤",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest6919821272198102839.description1":"&7该仪式能将&b天气&7设置为&1雨天&7。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest6919821272198102839.subtitle":"偏逢连夜雨",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest6919821272198102839.task.867668974944365052.title":"任意#minecraft:sand",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest6919821272198102839.title":"&6下雨天",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest6943496735150298785.description1":"&7&6异界树苗交易者&7可用普通树苗交换&d稳定版本的异界树苗&7，无需&b“第三只眼”&7也能收获。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest6943496735150298785.subtitle":"异界生活",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest6943496735150298785.title":"&6异界树苗交易者",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest7040476626497107504.description1":"&7觉得你的&d巨灵&7干得不够好？",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest7040476626497107504.description2":"&7嗯……说真的，他们连薪水都没有。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest7040476626497107504.description3":"&7但是没问题！直接用&c火灵矿工&7替代它们！",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest7040476626497107504.subtitle":"火灵矿工",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest7040476626497107504.title":"&6更好的矿工",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest7051665384546628144.description1":"&7虽然&4&o不是必须的&r&7，但我推荐在深入研究&5神秘学&7之前，完成&6所有右侧分支&7的基础内容。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest7051665384546628144.description2":"&7某些&5仪式&7也需要做好准备，它们需要&c强大的魔灵&7。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest7051665384546628144.description3":"&7记得研读你的&b魔灵全典&7——其中可能包含了对你取得成功至关重要的信息。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest7051665384546628144.subtitle":"踏入未知",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest7051665384546628144.task.3910792842216289124.title":"更广泛的神秘",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest7051665384546628144.title":"&6更广泛的神秘",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest7065751728094472376.description1":"&7帮助其他&6使魔&7，防止&c使魔死亡&7，还能吸取&4敌人生命力&7。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest7065751728094472376.subtitle":"长相怪异的妖精",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest7065751728094472376.task.3782662798827546770.title":"看向一个妖精使魔",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest7065751728094472376.title":"&6妖精使魔",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest7127714771743727494.description1":"&7生成小号的自己协助&c战斗&7。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest7127714771743727494.subtitle":"老鼠？",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest7127714771743727494.task.6583180429126610644.title":"看向一个莎布·尼古拉丝使魔",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest7127714771743727494.title":"&6莎布·尼古拉丝使魔",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest7194615247323750013.description1":"&7&6维度矿井&7能够从&d挖矿维度&7自动挖掘矿石！",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest7194615247323750013.subtitle":"通向挖矿维度的虫洞",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest7194615247323750013.title":"&6维度矿井",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest7200611429038054778.description1":"&7&6魔精清洁工&7是一种召唤魔灵，能够&a收集掉落物&7并将其放入&e链接的容器&7中，非常干净利落。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest7200611429038054778.description2":"&7一个谦卑的助手，让物品保持&b干净整洁&7。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest7200611429038054778.subtitle":"清洁小队",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest7200611429038054778.title":"&6魔精清洁工",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest7205753566080230259.description1":"&7你知道其实有两种制作&6绑定之书：空&7的方式吗？",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest7205753566080230259.description2":"&7只需将一个&f书与笔&7扔进&5灵火&7，或者用老方法，将三个材料不用染料直接合成。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest7205753566080230259.description3":"&7它们便于存储，以备后用！（译者注：此物品在翻译时仍无官方或CFPA提供的译名，故在子标题中保留物品原名，便于搜索）",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest7205753566080230259.subtitle":"Book Of Binding: Empty",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest7205753566080230259.task.463495614613140134.title":"你知道吗？",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest7205753566080230259.title":"&e你知道吗？",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest7233672429995629906.description1":"&7使用&5海德林诱惑术&7召唤&6被附身的末影螨&7，击杀以获取&d末地石&7。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest7233672429995629906.description2":"&7向仪式圈内扔一个&f鸡蛋&7来启动仪式。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest7233672429995629906.description3":"&7&o不要点击&6献祭之碗&7——这会干扰仪式的进行。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest7233672429995629906.subtitle":"末地石",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest7233672429995629906.title":"&6被附身的末影螨",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest7245643308122934904.description1":"&7召唤一只&5被附身的恶魂&7，它能够掉落&61-3个恶魂之泪&7。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest7245643308122934904.subtitle":"下界之泪",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest7245643308122934904.title":"&6被附身的恶魂",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest7271250144237883672.description1":"&7啊？哦……是&a你&7，很好。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest7271250144237883672.description2":"&7我怎么又回来了？啊……什么东西都要我说明一下吗？",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest7271250144237883672.description3":"&7那是一个&4未约束的火灵&7——也许是你们人类面对的最强大的东西。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest7271250144237883672.description4":"&7重要的是，它身上的材料可以让你制作出&c红色粉笔&7，用来绘制大后期的&5仪式&7。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest7271250144237883672.description5":"&7我现在能回去接着看电视了吧？很好，&7离我远点！",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest7271250144237883672.subtitle":"强大的对手",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest7271250144237883672.title":"&4<shake>未约束的火灵",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest7324192519006302133.description1":"&7该仪式能将&e时间&7设置为&5黄昏&7。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest7324192519006302133.subtitle":"晚上好",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest7324192519006302133.task.3864390130494194285.title":"任意#balm:black_dyes",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest7324192519006302133.task.395303570975822339.title":"任意#mekanism:colorable/beds",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest7324192519006302133.task.6761750026056888598.title":"任意#forge:bones",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest7324192519006302133.title":"&6日落黄昏",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest7493375611196176508.description1":"&7提供&c抗火&7，且能攻击敌人。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest7493375611196176508.subtitle":"被诅咒的灵魂",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest7493375611196176508.task.3976453255961768645.title":"看向一个恶魔使魔",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest7493375611196176508.title":"&6恶魔使魔",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest7752461306823572143.description1":"&7&6虫洞&7能够让你远程访问存储空间——",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest7752461306823572143.description2":"&7甚至可以跨&d维度&7访问！",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest7752461306823572143.subtitle":"维度传输",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest7752461306823572143.title":"&6虫洞",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest8040964005359393824.description1":"&7&6存储访问器&7可以让你远程访问存储空间！",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest8040964005359393824.description2":"&7是不是很有用？&7拜拜，背包！",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest8040964005359393824.subtitle":"便携式存储",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest8040964005359393824.title":"&6手持黑洞",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest8273544086428870792.description1":"&7干得好！你刚刚创造了第一个属于你的&6魔精碎矿者&7！",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest8273544086428870792.description2":"&7你已经掌握了基础——但你还有其他事情要做，而现在你多了一个&a朋友&7来帮助你！",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest8273544086428870792.description3":"&7给你的碎矿者提供矿石或岩石，它就能产出&6粉碎矿石&7，粉碎矿石在之后的制作中至关重要。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest8273544086428870792.description4":"&7例如：给碎矿者扔&6三个金锭&7来制作&6金色粉笔&7！（译者注：副标题来自表示猫肥胖度的meme，其中最胖的等级就是“我的天，他要把我压烂了”）",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest8273544086428870792.subtitle":"我的天，他要把我压烂了",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest8273544086428870792.task.4010957439608146160.title":"任意#forge:dusts/gold",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest8273544086428870792.title":"&6粉碎工作！",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest8275902639326351017.description1":"&7由于&6传送石&7在游戏后期才能获得，将你的&5神秘学存储系统&7链接到其他系统一并使用会更简单，比如&d新生魔艺&7。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest8275902639326351017.subtitle":"一些平替",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest8275902639326351017.title":"&e其他远程存储方式",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest8381513675094618102.description1":"&7创造属于你自己的&5灵火&7，只需将&d魔鬼之梦果&7扔在地上，并用&6打火石&7对其点火即可。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest8381513675094618102.description2":"&7不需要想太多——这种神秘的火焰&a不会扩散&7，&a不会自己熄灭&7，也&a不会烧伤你&7。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest8381513675094618102.description3":"&7下一步，将&6安山岩&7直接扔进&5灵火&7里。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest8381513675094618102.description4":"&7片刻之后，它们就会被火焰吞噬，转化为来自异界的&6石头&7。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest8381513675094618102.subtitle":"我的火是紫色的？！",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest8381513675094618102.task.6145697974335675553.title":"创造灵火",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest8381513675094618102.title":"&6灵火",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest844742277781913215.description1":"&7所幸，这个&5仪式&7相当简单——甚至不需要献祭。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest844742277781913215.description2":"&7但之后的仪式可能需要。如果仪式圈内出现&7灰色粒子&7，就说明需要进行献祭。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest844742277781913215.description3":"&7在仪式附近杀死祭品即可开始仪式。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest844742277781913215.description4":"&7你可以使用&d灵魂宝石&7（之后会提到）来转移祭品，不必再用&6矿车&7了！",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest844742277781913215.subtitle":"代罪羔羊",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest844742277781913215.task.6702997932158709621.title":"&6小窍门",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest844742277781913215.title":"&e小窍门",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest8696452092533015343.description1":"&7提供&b多段跳&7、&b跳跃提升&7和&b缓降&7。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest8696452092533015343.subtitle":"异界鹦鹉",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest8696452092533015343.task.8679000043911424155.title":"看向一个具翼使魔",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest8696452092533015343.title":"&6具翼使魔",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest9220715628425286255.description1":"&7你知道其实&e其他蜡烛&7也可以使用吗？",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest9220715628425286255.description2":"&7尽情尝试吧——&5异界&7没那么挑剔！",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest9220715628425286255.subtitle":"色彩！",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest9220715628425286255.task.3992669878333216873.title":"你知道吗？",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest9220715628425286255.title":"&e你知道吗？",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest938629473714937137.description1":"&7挖掘&6艾瑟金属&7并不困难！",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest938629473714937137.description2":"&7用&6探测杖&7潜行右击&4下界岩&7进行同调。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest938629473714937137.description3":"&7然后松开潜行，到你的&c下界合金&7矿道里长按鼠标右键——附近的&6艾瑟金属&7将被高亮显示！",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest938629473714937137.description4":"&7记得用&6灌注镐&7挖掘！",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest938629473714937137.subtitle":"艾瑟矿工",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest938629473714937137.title":"&6艾瑟金属",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest982204521289093032.description1":"&7啊哦！还不够多？彳亍——",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest982204521289093032.description2":"&7你可以通过几个&5仪式&7升级你的&6存储稳定器&7！",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest982204521289093032.subtitle":"满满当当",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.quest982204521289093032.title":"&6等级2存储稳定器",
    "ftbquests.chapter.occultism.title":"&7神秘学"
}